Key Takeaways
One of the biggest lessons from this project was understanding how ensemble learning methods such as Gradient Boosting can significantly improve predictive performance by combining the strengths of multiple decision trees.

The project also reinforced the importance of data preparation and evaluation metrics, as model performance depends not only on the algorithm itself but also on the quality of the underlying data and the way results are measured.

